{"tid":1328710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田回顧，由方陣戰變咗做半游擊戰","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:47:06.000Z","uid":90735,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe48d2b50532c53ea50ad692593a537154d2b4b","tid":1328710,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:02:57.000Z","msg":"<strong>源禾路方陣對峙</strong><br />\n示威者：築防線、遮、磚、紙皮盾<br />\n防暴：所有正規裝備，本來勝算大<br />\n<br />\n<strong>演變成商場游擊戰</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YREJ6LgYPfY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYREJ6LgYPfY&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=82b61ecd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YREJ6LgYPfY</a><br />\n2:04 <strong>游擊戰要點出現：</strong>居民支持你，會幫你帶路，所以好運中心走得甩 (所以去東區嘅話，藍絲有晒制空權)<br />\n2:28 警察傻傻哋入咗去<strong>無制空權</strong>嘅地方，唔洗請都入咗甕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後大家都知發生乜事，入到新城市廣場。警察一開始無制空權，用唔到方陣推進，同時驚誤傷普通市民，武器選擇少，個別嘅警察走散被市民圍剿<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上謹為事實陳述，及新聞分析"},{"pid":"da509601e3358c68759b5c11473f1039a4b74cf3","tid":1328710,"uid":90735,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:06:49.000Z","msg":"方陣 VS 游擊，部署+心態好唔同<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5756cfb1d0be002f41dfa0a7670b47e934b1d238","tid":1328710,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455ee1ce56fbe2b62f3ba94ed9a93d2c9882b833","tid":1328710,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83643894d24885d7318cd322e42e595bdf1906f1","tid":1328710,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"